events.text: I don’t know what to do. What’s happening to me?! Walking takes so long and it’s so tiring!
Oh, I’ve always wanted a cat. They are so cute. Hello, kitty kitty kitty…
Omg, omg, I am dying. Sooooo many stairs.
This also doesn’t work?!? I have to use the actual key to open my apartment door?! What the hell is going on. I am seriously getting worried.
